<div id="comments" class="comment-list hot show">
        <ul>
                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="869598205">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-869598205" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-869598205" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="869598205">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/leoyin1989/">白鹇</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2014-12-16</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">作者的饼摊得略大，两百多页的篇幅研究十个人物，难免浮于表面，但表述尚可，入门性著作。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="940127448">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-940127448" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-940127448" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="940127448">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/atee66/">黄瓜皮蛋汤</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-07-14</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">最近几年读到的少有的思想史佳作之一，出自青年学人之手。功力相当了得，文笔也相当典雅。只是感觉缺乏一条大线条贯穿全书。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="869651343">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-869651343" class="vote-count">0</span>
